Use Case 2: Loyalty Status App Push Notification

Cumulus Bank and Financial Services wants to use MobilePush to send an app notification to customers who have reached Gold loyalty status, and they're eligible to redeem a $100 gift card from their favorite food delivery service.

Let's review the solution steps for this campaign.

Establish Campaign Requirements
Identify campaign goals
Send an app notification when a customer's reward status changes to Gold.
As a reward for becoming a Gold member, inform customers of the redeemable gift card.
The campaign is ongoing, regularly adding customers who meet the criteria.
Identify personalization components
The app message includes the customer's first name, previous loyalty status, new loyalty status, and the gift card reward bonus.
Identity audience and data sources
Active customers whose loyalty level has changed in the past 7 days.
Unified Individual, Loyalty Program Member, and Loyalty Member Tier data sources.
Gather campaign materials
Compose the copy for the app message in Marketing Cloud Engagement.
